title: Mask of Dust (1954) Action, Adventure, Drama | Full length movie

sources.title: Mask of Dust (1954) Action, Adventure, Drama | Full length movie
sources.description:
A car pilot must choose between his love for car-racing, and his wife. His buddy's accident will help him to choose, and his loyal ways will get him a new friend - his main rival.

Director: Terence Fisher
Writers: Jon Manchip White, Paul Tabori, Richard H. Landau
Stars: Richard Conte, Mari Aldon, Peter Illing
Genres: Action, Adventure, Drama, Sport
